ts/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d89fcd5b96a4460e0cf1184f111795fb71fb3c","tid":61104,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明六四後係好好既時機爭取更多居英權或香港全面自治全面普選、甚至獨立<br />\n但最後乜都無等「民主回歸」<br />\n真係好on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇睇清楚啲文件<br />\n全部都係因為支共反對，英方就鳩縮<br />\n再者當年西方要聯支圍蘇<br />\n香港咪犧牲下囉"},{"pid":"84b900ce3db2309c22b3eb6aa8dd4d2257a93757","tid":61104,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"指香港商界對中方的暴力鎮壓表示憤慨，但同時認為要保持中港商業往來，因他們在內地已投資了大量廠房。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b4667da8ac5966ee6508a3615414437ed26bae","tid":61104,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c566322bc8b2104083a68757ae4c6ffb4f41466e","tid":61104,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來早有預備，當年唔衝去蝕咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要怪就怪個班70 80後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n80後得10幾歲，點去？主要係啲50-60後沉醉當時香港樓價暴升帶嚟嘅快感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果陣香港大正la,正常人係唔理呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74db0bc5795384b539aeee03aea5a6db99a2eb54","tid":61104,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"如果928果晚開左槍, 情況會點??"},{"pid":"e586464a919b648affe5ecf46c73bd93a2bdccd7","tid":61104,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六四事件爆發後，港人對中共政權信心盡失，掀起大規模移民潮，民間要求賦予居英權的訴求愈趨強烈。英國解